channel.title: Audacious 718 || Brand New RSPS! || Looking for staff ||
channel.description:
[center][size=14pt][font=georgia]Welcome to Audacious![/font][/size] Audacious is a brand new rsps I set up just for fun! I am currently looking for moderators, administrators and developers! I will put more time into this thread tomorrow when I've more time.
[size=14pt][font=georgia]Download Link:[/font][/size] https://www.dropbox.com/s/yn9cd53s7c8yi18/Audacious.jar?dl=0
[size=14pt][font=georgia]Website & Forums: [size=14pt][font=georgia]Coming Soon!
[size=14pt][font=georgia]Features:[/font][/size] [spoiler]Fully working Grand Exchange. All 25 skills work. Master capes for every skill. Fully working dungeoneering - 100% - Party's. Duel Arena. Clan & Friends Chat! Ticket System. Notes 100%. Various Skilling Locations! 5 Fun minigames! 13+ Fun bosses to fight! And much much more!![/spoiler]
